                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15/1129: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gibson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-11-22T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 22, 1930—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>10. Your 33, November 21, noon. Department considers the draft quoted
                    satisfactory and appreciates the reasons cited for the additions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
